      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied this car since day one, and it's in truly pristine condition inside and out. If you're looking for something that's been cared for with a lot of love and is ready for its next adventure, this is the one. Come say hi and take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
