    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1987 Carrera 3.2 represents the pinnacle of G-Series development, featuring the coveted Getrag G50 five-speed transaxle with Borg-Warner synchronizers for flawless gear selection. The naturally aspirated 3.2L flat-six delivers linear power through a perfectly calibrated Bosch Motronic DME system, with zero evidence of oil weeping from the crankcase or cylinder heads. The chassis maintains its structural integrity with original torsion bar suspension and factory-spec alignment, while the staggered Fuchs forged alloys remain free of curb rash. This specimen retains all original VIN tags and factory-applied coatings, presenting a level of mechanical and aesthetic preservation that satisfies the most demanding concours standards.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
