    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of the widebody, naturally aspirated 911. Powered by a 3.6L flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus, the engine provides immediate throttle response and a linear torque curve. The mechanical integrity is beyond reproach; the IMS bearing has been proactively replaced with a permanent dual-row ceramic solution, and the rear main seal is perfectly dry. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed manual transaxle and a viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system that ensures exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with original-equipment Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings throughout. The cooling system has been optimized with a low-temperature thermostat to ensure thermal stability. This vehicle has been maintained to a concours standard, with zero oxidation on the undercarriage and factory-spec compression across all cylinders. A turn-key acquisition for the discerning enthusiast seeking a mechanically flawless driving machine.",
